Comment: 1,0:02:04.02,0:02:04.52,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Hey
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.65,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,開端便是一切都順序錯亂
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.65,0:02:09.52,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,一成不變的生活地覆天翻
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.52,0:02:12.28,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,很久很久很久以前
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.28,0:02:15.40,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,人還知吃吃喝喝舞中作樂
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.40,0:02:17.74,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,今辛酸痛苦無止境  社會壓力超負荷
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.74,0:02:20.78,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,早間新聞將這常態播放著
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.78,0:02:22.49,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,逼著我睜開雙眼  漱口洗臉
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.49,0:02:25.25,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,早餐一個漢堡打發  能不能來點奇蹟使天地異變
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.25,0:02:26.75,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,做什麼夢呢我傻嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.75,0:02:27.96,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Song of the dead
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.08,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Song of the dead
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.08,0:02:29.58,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,I wanna!!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.58,0:02:31.00,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dancing, dancing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.42,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Rolling, rolling
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.76,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Only one, my life
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.76,0:02:38.05,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,不久後人生即將畫上句號
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.05,0:02:41.05,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,僅有空虛又怎夠將我填飽？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.05,0:02:42.31,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dancing dancing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.31,0:02:43.81,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Morning morning
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.81,0:02:49.19,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,立足原點  保持新鮮
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.19,0:02:52.36,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,做我所願
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.36,0:02:55.19,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Every night, every time
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.19,0:03:02.28,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,活至盡興  玩到疲倦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.66,0:03:06.25,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dystopia to song of the dead!!
